import { gql } from "apollo-server";

// synchronize prisma
export default gql`
    type User {
        id : String!
        firstName : String!
        lastName : String
        username : String!
        email : String!
        createdAt : String!
        updatedAt : String!
        bio : String
        avatar : String
        following : [User]
        followers : [User]
        totalFollowing : Int!
        totalFollowers : Int!
        isFollowing : Boolean!
        isMe : Boolean!               
    }
`
